Former president Donald #Trump and rapper #YoungThug might have more in common than it appears!

As you may already know, on Monday (Aug. 14) Donald Trump – alongside 18 co-defendants – made headlines for being indicted in Georgia over his efforts to overturn the 2020 election. Fulton County District Attorney Fani Willis filed racketeering charges against the defendants that claim their post-election actions were part of a criminal enterprise. In addition to the #RICO charge, Trump was hit with 13 separate criminal counts in the new indictment.

This includes solicitation of violation of oath by a public officer, conspiracy to commit impersonating a public officer, conspiracy to commit forgery in the first degree, conspiracy to commit false statements and writings, and conspiracy to commit filing false documents.

The 18 others named in the indictment are Trevian Kutti, former publicist for R. Kelly and Kanye West, Rudy Giuliani, John Eastman, Mark Meadows, Kenneth Chesebro, Jeffrey Clark, Jenna Ellis, Ray Smith III, Robert Cheeley, Michael Roman, David Shafer, Shawn Still, Stephen Lee, Harrison Floyd, Sidney Powell, Cathleen Latham, Scott Hall, and Misty Hampton (aka Emily Misty Hayes).

During a news conference last night, Willis revealed that arrest warrants have been issued and all the defendants have until noon on Aug. 25 to turn themselves over to authorities. Trump’s latest legal troubles may come as no surprise as he’s now been charged in four separate cases surrounding his presidency, according to reports.

However, you may be a little shocked to learn that Fani Willis is the same D.A. who brought RICO charges against Rapper Young Thug. As previously reported, last May the “Day Before” rhymer was among 28 people associated with #YSL who were charged in a 56-count Racketeer Influenced and Corrupt Organizations Act indictment. Young Thug’s legal team has tried multiple times to get him released on bond, however, they have yet to be successful in their attempts… Full story on #thejasminebrand.com

لا شيء يعبر عن الرومانسية كالورد. 
الورد بشكله ثلاثي الابعاد يعود كموضة من موضات الألفيه منذ موسم ولم يبرح حتى إجتاح اسبوع الازياء الراقية كاملاً. 
ارماني بريڤيه، هذا الرجل الذي يعرف بحق معنى الكوتور الاصيل ومعنى الاناقة الخالدة للمرأة. يقدم هذا الموسم ازياء وفساتين كلاسيكية تزينها الورود بشكل رومانسي حالم. 
ومن ثم يأتي راهول ميشرا ليجعل من العارضة "وردة" بذاتها تسير على ممر الازياء. 
واما ڤالنتينو، فالورد جزء لا يتجزأ من هوية الدار لذلك دوماً مانراه حاضراً في الطبعات او كتشكيل بشكل ثلاثي الابعاد كما ظهر هذا الموسم. 

Flora Couture 
Nothing says romance like flowers.
Flowers in its 3D form returned as a fashion trend from the 00s during RTW shows last season, and it did not stop until it invaded the entire Haute Couture week.
Armani Privé, truly knows the meaning of authentic couture and the meaning of timeless elegance for women. This season offers classic silhouettes and dresses adorned with flowers in a romantic, dreamy way.
And then comes Rahul Mishra to make the model an actual flower walking down the runway.
As for Valentino, flowers are an essence part of the maison’s dna, so we always see it present in motifs as well as a 3D formation this season.

Summer vacation Day2🌀☁️🗻☁️
台風の影響でずーっとお天気は曇ったりいきなり雨が降ったり、変わりやすい雲が厚い空でした☁️折角の山中湖泊でしたが、シャイな富士山は、足元しか見せてもらえず雄大な姿は見れずでした〜あぁー残念😓
雲が厚かったので、あまり日焼けの心配はなく、過ごしやすいお天気の二日目は、忍野八海に観光に行きました！湧池などがかなりのパワースポットということで、沢山パワーを注入して、気持ち良かった✨そのあとは、お買い物へ🛍️✨ここで弾きが強い私は、かねてから欲しかった憧れのハイヒールが…な、なんと⁈アウトレットで発見💡表参道の店舗ではサイズが無く、シーズンカラーだったので諦めていたが、まさかここで現品限りが、私のサイズで、まさにシンデレラ気分👠✨MANOLOのショッキングピンクのハイヒール💖出会いに感動して私の元にきてくれてありがとうと🥺本当に嬉しかったぁ〜。また、VALENTINOでも、素敵なハイヒールとその靴に合うバックをセットで購入。仕事を頑張ろうと思えるキッカケ、モチベーションをいただいたショッピング🛍️Life is short … 年齢に抗いながらも着たいものを着て履きたいもの履く、女性としてお洒落を楽しんで人生を謳歌したいと思う❣️一度きりの人生。一生懸命働いて、家族の為、自分の為に頑張ろうと、また気持ちを整え、心身共にリフレッシュした旅でした💖Thanks Maco❤️
